 honest stable equilibria by\nincreasing the reward-punishment ratio and lowering both the cost-punishment\nratio and the pivotality rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Dec 2022 19:56:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 18:00:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2023 22:21:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-23"}
